        <dd class="mt-1 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
          <p class="flex-auto">
            Connect with stakeholders and build relationships to drive change. Use Obsekio to identify key players in your network and understand the relationships between them.                
          </p>
        </dd>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col">
        <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-white">
          <div class="mb-6 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-yellow-500">
            <%= render_icon :open_source %>
          </div>
          Community driven
        </dt>
        <dd class="mt-1 flex flex-auto flex-col text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
          <p class="flex-auto">Obsekio is an open-source project designed with community needs at its core. It thrives on collaborative input, ensuring the software evolves to serve and benefits the community.</p>
        </dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div> 
